casebody.data:
Third Department,

January, 1978

(January 5, 1978) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Charles Cannavino, Appellant.

Motion by appellant to strike copy of Grand Jury minutes submitted with respondent’s brief and for other relief, denied, without costs (see People v Longo, 39 AD2d 633). Mahoney, P. J., Greenblott, Sweeney, Kane and Mikoll, JJ., concur.
